title: What is Ornn????
body:
[http://universe.leagueoflegends.com/en_US/region/freljord/?mv=freljord-song](http://universe.leagueoflegends.com/en_US/region/freljord/?mv=freljord-song)
In the link we see the teaser to the next League of Legends champion Ornn. While reading the passage about it seems as if Ornn could be a tank not only that but the last tank released was Tahm Kench on July 9, 2015 it has been over 2 years since we have seen a new tank which makes it likely Ornn will a Primary tank. If Ornn isn't a tank he could be an assassin because the last primary assassin released was kindred 10/14/2015 which is reaching the 2 years since a new assassin has been released.
Please give me your Thoughts on what Ornn could be.
Thank you for reading.
